sequenceDiagram
    participant User
    participant ALB
    participant App as Private App EC2
    participant DB as Data Placeholder EC2

    User->>ALB: HTTP GET /
    ALB->>App: Forward request on port 80
    App->>App: Read instance metadata
    App->>DB: TCP connection to port 5432
    DB-->>App: Connection accepted
    App-->>ALB: HTML response
    ALB-->>User: HTTP 200

    User->>ALB: HTTP GET /health
    ALB->>App: Health check request
    App-->>ALB: ok
    ALB-->>User: HTTP 200
